sequenceDiagram
    participant MLApp as ML Application
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OnlineSvc as Online Store Service<br/>80/443/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>OIDC/RBAC (optional)
    participant Redis as Redis<br/>6379/TCP<br/>TLS1.2+ (optional)
    participant Registry as Registry Server<br/>6570-6571/TCP gRPC/HTTP<br/>TLS1.2+ (optional)
    participant Offline as Offline Store<br/>8815-8816/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant CronJob as Materialization CronJob

    Note over MLApp,Registry: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval (Real-time Inference)

    MLApp->>Route: POST /get-online-features<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OIDC)
    Route->>OnlineSvc: Forward Request<br/>TLS Termination
    OnlineSvc->>Registry: Query Feature Metadata<br/>gRPC/HTTP
    Registry-->>OnlineSvc: Feature Schema
    OnlineSvc->>Redis: Fetch Pre-computed Features<br/>Password Auth (optional)
    Redis-->>OnlineSvc: Feature Values
    OnlineSvc-->>Route: JSON Response
    Route-->>MLApp: Feature Vector

    Note over MLApp,S3: Flow 2: Historical Feature Retrieval (Model Training)

    MLApp->>Offline: POST /get-historical-features<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    Offline->>Registry: Query Feature Definitions<br/>gRPC/HTTP
    Registry-->>Offline: Feature Metadata
    Offline->>S3: Read Historical Parquet Data<br/>AWS IAM Auth
    S3-->>Offline: Historical Features
    Offline-->>MLApp: Historical Feature Dataset

    Note over CronJob,Redis: Flow 3: Feature Materialization (Scheduled)

    CronJob->>Offline: Fetch Latest Feature Data<br/>Service Account Token
    Offline->>S3: Query Offline Store<br/>HTTPS/AWS IAM
    S3-->>Offline: Raw Feature Data
    Offline-->>CronJob: Computed Features
    CronJob->>OnlineSvc: Write Materialized Features<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    OnlineSvc->>Redis: Store Features<br/>Redis Protocol
    Redis-->>OnlineSvc: ACK
    OnlineSvc-->>CronJob: Success
